headline: Equifax Introduces Equifax Ignite® AI Advisor
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) announces the launch of Equifax Ignite® AI Advisor, a new solution designed to help lenders pinpoint new opportunities, grow accounts, and make confident informed decisions at speed on one platform. Powered by a secure Agentic-AI enabled data and analytics engine on the Equifax Cloud™, Equifax Ignite AI Advisor is built with Equifax Amplify AI™.
